            "required": true,
            "options": null,
            "is_constituent_info": false,
            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Supports high-tech aerospace manufacturing and safety services in the 33rd District through recent contract recipients including Fieldtech Avionics & Instruments Inc ($31,666) and Koetter Fire Protection International, LLC ($22,695).\n* Sustains a local talent pipeline of STEM professionals and entrepreneurs who contribute to the broader North Texas aerospace and technology economy.\n* Contributes to the national 3:1 return on investment for NASA spending, which drives innovation and economic activity across the district.",
