            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* This programmatic request provides $9 billion for NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD) to fund Earth Science, Planetary Science, Astrophysics, Heliophysics, and Biological and Physical Sciences.\n* Funding ensures the execution of National Academies' Decadal Survey priorities, which represent the scientific community's peer-reviewed consensus on the most vital questions for American exploration.\n* Supports critical mission development and operations that provide essential data for national security, weather forecasting, and planetary defense.",
