            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Restoring and stabilizing NASA Science funding is essential to recover from the workforce disruptions and layoffs resulting from the FY 2026 budget environment.\n* Sustained investment is a strategic necessity to maintain U.S. leadership in space science and set the norms for exploration as international competitors like China rapidly expand their lunar and planetary ambitions.\n* NASA Science delivers outsized returns in discovery and national prestige for less than one-third of one percent of federal spending.",
